Entries.Text: Shadow bathes in light and knows weakness
The Cave of Knowledge lies below

I'm bound northways for Liurnia.
May fate find us doing business again.

There's a traitor taken care of.
Onwards to Nokron, then.
Go on. I'll catch up.

Find yourself maidenless?
Off to Liurnia with you, then!
Seek the Rose Church, west of the Gate Town.
Surely what you seek is somewhere close by...
Rainbow Stones lead the way to riches...
Stop by the shack beyond the southern gate

I'm bound northways for Leyndell.
May fate find us doing business again.
Seek the western edge of the main road
Seek a shattered bridge at the top of a bypath

Though the path be broken and uncertain,
claim your place as Elden Lord!
A chamber lies under the ruins

Far to the east, you'll find
the Cathedral of Dragon Communion.
A place where draconic power gathers.
I'll defile you next. Come to the outer moat.

I thought this a mountain of fire,
but I hardly feel a thing!
I'll have to head further down...

I will return to the academy, my apprentice.
To expel the Carian royal family,
and restore the primeval current.
